ZH: 为了学好英语，我每天都要练习阅读和写作。
EN: In order to become fluent in English, I practice reading and writing every day.

ZH: 为了庆祝生日，我决定去海滩度假。
EN: In order to celebrate my birthday, I decided to go on a beach vacation.

