EN: In order to protect the environment, we should reduce the use of plastic bags.

ZH: 为了追求梦想，他放弃了稳定的工作。
EN: In order to pursue his dreams, he gave up a stable job.

ZH: 为了提高生产效率，公司引入了新的技术。
EN: In order to improve production efficiency, the company introduced new technology.

ZH: 为了帮助贫困地区的孩子，他们捐赠了很多书籍和教材。
EN: In order to help children in impoverished areas, they donated many books and teaching materials.

ZH: 为了保持健康，他每天都去健身房锻炼。
EN: In order to stay healthy, he goes to the gym to exercise every day.

ZH: 为了更好地了解中国文化，她决定学习汉语。
EN: In order to better understand Chinese culture, she decided to learn Mandarin.

