EN: In order to avoid risks, investors diversify their investments in the stock market.

ZH: 为了增加销售额，商家通过广告和促销活动吸引顾客。
EN: In order to increase sales, retailers attract customers through advertising and promotional activities.

ZH: 为了节约时间，她在周末做好了所有的家务。
EN: In order to save time, she did all the housework on the weekend.

ZH: 为了培养孩子的兴趣，他们报了一个音乐课程。
EN: In order to cultivate their child's interest, they enrolled in a music course.

ZH: 为了赶上最后一班车，他匆匆忙忙地出门了。
EN: In order to catch the last bus, he hurriedly left home.

